# Normalize all text to LF on checkout, on every OS. Without this, Windows
# (core.autocrlf=true) rewrites files to CRLF after checkout, which git then
# sees as local modifications — blocking the auto-update `git pull`/sync and
# leaving clients stuck on an old version. The launcher also `reset --hard`s as
# a belt-and-braces safeguard.
* text=auto eol=lf
